Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     ShippingMethodDraft shippingMethodDraft = ShippingMethodDraft.builder()
             .name("{name}")
             .taxCategory(taxCategoryBuilder -> taxCategoryBuilder)

             .isDefault(true)
             .build()
